{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SVG教學","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/SVG\">SVG</a>是W3C XML的方言之一，用於標記可縮放的向量圖形。目前在Firefox、Opera、Webkit瀏覽器、IE等瀏覽器中已經部分實作。</p>\n\n<p>本教學之目標在解釋SVG內部的技術細節。如果你只是想要畫出漂亮的圖形，你可以在<a href=\"http://inkscape.org/doc/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Inkscape的文件頁面</a>上找到更多有用的資源。或是看看另一個好的SVG介绍：<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/IG/resources/svgprimer.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C的SVG入門</a>。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">本教學文件還在初期階段，如果你有能力，可以來增加擴展一兩段，寫一整頁的话會更好！</div>\n\n<h5 id=\"從頭介紹svg\">從頭介紹SVG</h5>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Introduction\">導論</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Getting_Started\">開始</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Positions\">坐標定位</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Basic_Shapes\">基本形状</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Paths\">路徑</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Fills_and_Strokes\">填充與邊框</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Gradients\">漸變</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Patterns\">模式</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Texts\">文字</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Basic_Transformations\">基本變换</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Clipping_and_masking\">裁剪和遮罩</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Other_content_in_SVG\">其他SVG内容</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects\">濾镜效果</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_fonts\">SVG字型</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_Image_Tag\">SVG的Image標籤</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Tools_for_SVG\">SVG工具</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>下面陳列進階主题，需要單獨列出教學。</p>\n\n<h5 id=\"javascript脚本化svg\">JavaScript脚本化SVG</h5>\n\n<p>待定</p>\n\n<h5 id=\"svg濾镜教學\">SVG濾镜教學</h5>\n\n<p>待定</p>\n\n<h5 id=\"svg的smil動畫\">SVG的SMIL動畫</h5>\n\n<p>待定</p>\n\n<h5 id=\"在svg中建立字形\">在SVG中建立字形</h5>\n\n<p>待定</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"SVG是W3C XML的方言之一，用於標記可縮放的向量圖形。目前在Firefox、Opera、Webkit瀏覽器、IE等瀏覽器中已經部分實作。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Tutorial","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"SVG Tutorial","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Tutorial de SVG","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Tutoriel SVG","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SVG教本","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"SVG 튜토리얼","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"SVG Poradnik","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Tutorial SVG","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"SVG — учебное руководство","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"SVG 教程","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/svg/tutorial","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/svg/tutorial/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial","title":"SVG教學"}],"pageTitle":"SVG教學 - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}